Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有吗{\r}\NAnybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没人知道{\r}\NNot a clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}出自沃尔特・惠特曼为亚伯拉罕・林肯写的一首诗{\r}\NIt's from a poem by Walt Whitman about Mr Abraham Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}听好 在班上你们可以叫我基丁老师...{\r}\NNow in this class you can either call me Mr Keating...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}或者有胆量的话就叫"哦 船长 我的船长"{\r}\Nor, if you're slightly more daring, "O Captain, my Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我首先要消除一些谣言 免得误人子弟{\r}\NNow, let me dispel a few rumours so they don't fester into facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没错 我也上过这所地狱学校并活了下来{\r}\NYes, I, too, attended Hell-ton and survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不过 那时候我可不是你们现在看到的思想巨人{\r}\NAnd, no, at that time, I was not the mental giant you see before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我的智慧跟一个九十八磅重的弱智差不多{\r}\NI was the intellectual equivalent of a 98-pound weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我到海滩念诗 人们会把拜伦诗集往我脸上砸{\r}\NI would go to the beach, and people would kick copies of Byron in my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了... 皮茨{\r}\NNow... Mr Pitts?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这名字太不幸了{\r}\NThat's a rather unfortunate name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}皮茨 哪位是皮茨{\r}\NMr Pitts, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}皮茨 把诗集翻到第五百四十二页{\r}\NMr Pitts, would you open your hymnal to page 542.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}念一下那首诗的第一节{\r}\NRead the first stanza of the poem you find there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"劝少女们珍惜时光"{\r}\N"To the Virgins to Make Much of Time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对 就是那首{\r}\NYes, that's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对你们很合适 对吧{\r}\NSomewhat appropriate, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"及时采拮你的花蕾"{\r}\N"Gather ye rosebuds while ye may.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"旧时光一去不回"{\r}\N"Old Time is still a-flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"今天尚在微笑的花朵 明日便在风中枯萎"{\r}\NAnd this same flower that smiles today, tomorrow will be dying."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢你 皮茨{\r}\NThank you, Mr Pitts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"及时采拮你的花蕾"{\r}\N"Gather ye rosebuds while ye may."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这种感慨用拉丁语说 就叫"卡匹迪恩"{\r}\NThe Latin term for that sentiment is "Carpe diem."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有谁知道是什么意思吗{\r}\NNow, who knows what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"卡匹迪恩"也就是抓紧时间{\r}\NCarpe diem. That's "Seize the day."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 很好 你叫...  - 米克斯{\r}\N- Very good, Mister...  - Meeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}又一个不寻常的名字{\r}\NMeeks. Another unusual name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}抓紧时间{\r}\NSeize the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"及时采拮你的花蕾"{\r}\N"Gather ye rosebuds while ye may."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}为什么作者要写这几句话{\r}\NWhy does the writer use these lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 因为他很着急  - 不 叮{\r}\N- Because he's in a hurry.  - No! Ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不过还是要感谢你的幽默{\r}\NThank you for playing anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因为我们是蛆虫的食物{\r}\NBecause we are food for worms, lads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因为不管你信不信 在这儿的每一个人...{\r}\NBecause, believe it or not, each and every one of us in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有一天都会停止呼吸 变冷 死亡{\r}\Nis one day going to stop breathing, turn cold and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们到前面来{\r}\NI would like you to step forward over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:15:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好好看看过去的面孔{\r}\Nand peruse some of the faces from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们从这儿经过多次了{\r}\NYou've walked past them many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但肯定没有仔细看过{\r}\NI don't think you've really looked at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们和你们差别不大 对吧{\r}\NThey're not that different from you, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}同样的发型{\r}\NSame haircuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}充满活力 和你们一样{\r}\NFull of hormones, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}野心勃勃 和你们一样 世界在他们手中{\r}\NInvincible, just like you feel. The world is their oyster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}相信自己一定能成就伟大的事业 就像你们很多人一样{\r}\NThey believe they're destined for great things, just like many of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们眼中充满希望 就像你们一样{\r}\NTheir eyes are full of hope, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但他们是不是就曾经蹉跎而错过...{\r}\NDid they wait until it was too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们本可能成就的任何事业{\r}\Nto make from their lives even one iota of what they were capable?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因为 你瞧 各位 当年的年轻人已变成了花下之尘{\r}\NBecause, you see, gentlemen, these boys are now fertilizing daffodils.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但如果仔细听...{\r}\NBut if you listen real close...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们还能听见他们给你们留下的忠告{\r}\Nyou can hear them whisper their legacy to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}来吧 近一点听{\r}\NGo on, lean in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}听见了吗{\r}\NListen. Do you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}卡匹{\r}\NCarpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}听见了吗{\r}\NHear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}卡匹{\r}\NCarpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}卡匹迪恩{\r}\NCarpe diem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}抓紧时间 孩子们{\r}\NSeize the day, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}让你的生命不同寻常{\r}\NMake your lives extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 太怪了  - 但与众不同{\r}\N- That was weird.  - But different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是吓人 要我说的话{\r}\NSpooky, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你觉得这会考吗{\r}\NThink he'll test us on that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}行了 卡梅伦 你什么也没听明白{\r}\NOh, come on, Cameron. Don't you get anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}什么 什么{\r}\NWhat? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}走吧 孩子们 动作快点儿 说你呢 多尔顿{\r}\NLet's go, boys. Hustle up in here. That means you, Dalton!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 今晚几何学习小组谁参加{\r}\NWho's up for a quick study group tonight, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我  - 什么{\r}\N- Me.  - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我去不了了 今晚我得去丹伯里家吃饭{\r}\NI can't make it, guys. I have to have dinner at the Danburrys' house tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}丹伯里家 谁是丹伯里{\r}\NThe Danburrys? Who are the Danburrys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}废话 关你什么事{\r}\NBig alums. How'd you swing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我爸的朋友 可能都九十多岁了{\r}\NFriends of my dad's. They're probably in their nineties or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}总比呆在地狱学校强 诺克斯{\r}\NAnything's better than Hell-ton hash, Knox.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 说的没错  - 嗯 我们明白{\r}\N- I'll second that.  - Yeah, we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}今晚活动你参加吗{\r}\NYou coming to the study group tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 我... 有点历史作业要做{\r}\NUh... no. No, I... Uh, I've got some history I wanna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}随便你吧{\r}\NSuit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了吗 奥弗斯特里特{\r}\NReady, Overstreet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}可以走了{\r}\NReady to go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}切特 你去开门吧{\r}\NChet, can you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我忙着呢 妈  - 我去开{\r}\N- I can't, Mom.  - I'll get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}请问你找谁{\r}\NCan I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}嗨 我是诺克斯・奥弗斯特里特{\r}\NHi. Knox Overstreet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:19:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}黑格博士{\r}\NUh, Dr Hager.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是丹伯里家吧{\r}\NThis is the Danburrys', right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你是来找切特的  - 丹伯里太太{\r}\N- Are you here to see Chet?  - Mrs Danburry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 不  - 我是丹伯里太太{\r}\N- No.  - Sorry. Thank you. I'm Mrs Danburry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你是诺克斯吧  - 对{\r}\N- You must be Knox.  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}九点前回去 进来吧 快进来{\r}\NBack by 9:00? Please, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 克里丝 你在干嘛  - 切特 我来了{\r}\N- Chris, come on!  - Chet, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}诺克斯 你好吗 乔・丹伯里{\r}\NKnox. How are you? Joe Danburry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 很高兴见到您  - 他简直跟他父亲一个样{\r}\N- Nice to meet you, sir.  - He's the spitting image of his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 他怎么样 进来吧  - 克里丝{\r}\N- How is he? Come on in.  - Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 他挺好 刚办了件大案  - 这也是你的志向吧{\r}\N- Great. He just did a big case for G.M.  - I know where you're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我来了  - 有其父 必有其子{\r}\N- I'm coming.  - Like father, like son, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}神经病{\r}\NOoh! Psycho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 换个游戏玩  - 什么意思{\r}\N- Another game?  - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}用X和Y替换这些数字{\r}\Njust replace these numbers here with 'x, "for 'x"and 'y."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 当然  - 当然 那还有什么问题{\r}\N- Of course.  - Of course. So what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 等一下  - 吃得怎么样{\r}\N- Wait. No.  - How was dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 吃得怎么样  - 糟透了{\r}\N- How was dinner?  - Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:20:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 难受  - 为什么 出什么事了{\r}\N- Awful.  - Why? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}今晚 我见到了我一辈子见过的最漂亮的女孩{\r}\NTonight, I met the most beautiful girl I have ever seen in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你疯了吗 这有什么不好的{\r}\NAre you crazy? What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她差不多已经和切特・丹伯里订婚了{\r}\NShe's practically engaged to Chet Danburry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那家伙该死{\r}\NThat guy could eat a football.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 不好  - 不好{\r}\N- Too bad.  - "Too bad"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这比不好糟多了 这是个悲剧{\r}\NIt's worse than "too bad," Pittsie. It's a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这么漂亮的女孩居然爱上了那么个傻瓜{\r}\NA girl this beautiful in love with such a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}所有漂亮妞都喜欢傻瓜 这你知道{\r}\NAll the good ones go for jerks. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对 忘了她 打开你的几何书 想一下第五题{\r}\NYeah, forget her. Open your trig book and try and figure out problem five.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我忘不了她 卡梅伦{\r}\NI can't just forget her, Cameron.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}现在也不可能做几何题{\r}\NAnd I certainly can't think about trig.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}成功了{\r}\NWe got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 各位 五分钟{\r}\NAll right, gentlemen. Five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}走吧{\r}\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你见她裸体了吗  - 别胡说 多尔顿{\r}\N- Did you see her naked?  - Very funny, Dalton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你腿上不是个收音机吧{\r}\NThat wouldn't be a radio in your lap
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 皮茨  - 不是 科学实验{\r}\N- would it, Mr Pitts?  - No, sir. Science experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}雷达{\r}\NRadar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}各位 翻到前言第二十一页{\r}\NGentlemen, open your text to page 21 of the introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}佩里 你念一下序言{\r}\NMr Perry, will you read the opening paragraph of the preface
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"诗歌鉴赏"的第一段{\r}\Nentitled "Understanding Poetry."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"诗歌鉴赏" 作者 J・埃文斯・普里查特博士{\r}\N"'Understand Poetry" by Dr J. Evans Pritchard, Ph.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"要完全理解诗歌 我们首先必须了解..."{\r}\N"To fully understand poetry, we must first be fluent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"它的格调 韵律和修辞手法"{\r}\N"with its metre, rhyme and figures of speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"然后提两个问题"{\r}\N"Then ask two questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"第一 诗歌的主题是如何艺术地实现的"{\r}\N"One: How artfully has the objective of the poem been rendered?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"第二 该主题的重要性如何"{\r}\N'And, two: How important is that objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"第一个问题解决的是诗歌的艺术性"{\r}\N"Question one rates the poem's perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"第二个问题回答的是它的重要性"{\r}\N"Question two rates its importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"一旦弄清这两个问题"{\r}\N'And once these questions have been answered...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"判断该诗的优劣也就不是个太难的问题了"{\r}\N"determining a poem's greatness becomes a relatively simple matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"如果把诗歌艺术性的得分画在图表的横轴上"{\r}\N"If the poem's score for perfection is plotted on the horizontal of a graph...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"把它的重要性记在竖轴上"{\r}\N"and its importance is plotted on the vertical"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"计算一下所覆盖的面积"{\r}\N"then calculating the total area of the poem...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"也就得出了它的优劣"{\r}\N"yields the measure of its greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"拜伦的十四行诗可能在竖轴上得分很高"{\r}\N"A sonnet by Byron might score high on the vertical,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"但横向得分一般"{\r}\N"but only average on the horizontal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.71,0:22:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"而莎士比亚的十四行诗"{\r}\N'A Shakespearean sonnet, on the other hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"可能在横向和竖向上都得分很高"{\r}\N"would score high both horizontally and vertically,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"覆盖的面积很大"{\r}\Nyielding a massive total area
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"也就表明它是一首优秀的诗歌"{\r}\Nthereby revealing the poem to be truly great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"阅读本书的诗歌时 请练习这种分析方法"{\r}\N'As you proceed through the poetry in this book, practise this rating method.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.72,0:22:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"随着你用这种方法评价诗歌的能力不断提高"{\r}\N'As your ability to evaluate poems in this manner grows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.52,0:22:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"对诗歌的欣赏和理解也会日益提高"{\r}\Nso will... so will your enjoyment and understanding of poetry."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.74,0:22:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}屁话{\r}\NExcrement.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这就是我对 J・埃文斯・普里查特先生的评价{\r}\NThat's what I think of Mr J. Evans Pritchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.54,0:22:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们不是在安水管 我们是在谈论诗歌{\r}\NWe're not laying pipe. We're talking about poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我意思是 你怎么评论像美国诗人班德斯坦的诗呢{\r}\NI mean, how can you describe poetry like American Bandstand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.08,0:22:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"我喜欢拜伦 我给他四十二分 但并不为之欣喜"{\r}\N"I like Byron. I give him a 42. But I can't dance to it."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:23:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}现在 我要你们把那一页撕了{\r}\NNow, I want you to rip out that page.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.22,0:23:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}撕吧 把整页都撕了{\r}\NGo on. Rip out the entire page.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没听见吗 把它撕了{\r}\NYou heard me. Rip it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}把它撕了{\r}\NRip it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}快点 撕了它{\r}\NGo on. Rip it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢你 多尔顿{\r}\NThank you, Mr Dalton.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.44,0:23:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}各位 听我说 不只是要撕掉那一页{\r}\NGentlemen, tell you what. Don't just tear out that page.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.53,0:23:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}把整个前言都撕了 我不想再见到它{\r}\NTear out the entire introduction. I want it gone, history. Leave nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}全都撕了 撕了它 再见了{\r}\NRip it out! Rip! Be gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}J・埃文斯・普里查特博士{\r}\NJ. Evans Pritchard, Ph.D.!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}撕 扯 拽{\r}\NRip! Shred! Tear!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}撕了它 我只想听到撕书的声音{\r}\NRip it out! I want to hear nothing but ripping of Mr Pritchard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在上面打个孔串成一串{\r}\NWe'll perforate it, put it on a roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这不是《圣经》 你们不会因此下地狱{\r}\NIt's not the Bible. You're not gonna go to hell for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.26,0:23:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}继续 撕干净点儿 什么也不要剩{\r}\NGo on. Make a clean tear. I want nothing left of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.81,0:23:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不能损坏书籍{\r}\NWe shouldn't be doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.27,0:23:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}撕 撕 撕{\r}\NRip! Rip! Rip!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.81,0:23:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}撕了它 撕{\r}\NRip it out! Rip!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:24:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}撕了它 对 撕了它{\r}\NRip it! Yeah! Rip it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.62,0:24:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 撕了它  - 这是怎么回事{\r}\N- Rip it!  - What the hell is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 撕得还不够响  - 基丁先生{\r}\N- I don't hear enough rips.  - Mr Keating.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.67,0:24:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}麦卡利斯特先生{\r}\NMr McAllister.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.13,0:24:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对不起 我... 我不知道你在这儿{\r}\NI'm sorry, I... I didn't know you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.72,0:24:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我在  - 对不起{\r}\N- I am.  - Ah. So you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.68,0:24:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}打扰了{\r}\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.52,0:24:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}继续撕 各位{\r}\NKeep ripping, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.90,0:24:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是一场战斗 战争{\r}\NThis is a battle, a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.69,0:24:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}受害的可能是你们的思想和灵魂{\r}\NAnd the casualties could be your hearts and souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.86,0:24:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢你 多尔顿{\r}\NThank you, Mr Dalton.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.86,0:24:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}学院派在不断向诗歌发起进攻{\r}\NArmies of academics going forward measuring poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.03,0:24:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 我们不能答应{\r}\NNo! We will not have that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.03,0:24:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}让 J・埃文斯・普里查特见鬼去吧{\r}\NNo more of Mr J. Evans Pritchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.04,0:24:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}现在 各位你们要学会自己思考{\r}\NNow, my class, you will learn to think for yourselves again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.37,0:24:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们要学会欣赏文字和语言{\r}\NYou will learn to savour words and language.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.00,0:24:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不管别人怎么说{\r}\NNo matter what anybody tells you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.38,0:24:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}文字和语言的确能改变世界{\r}\Nwords and ideas can change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.22,0:25:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我发觉皮茨的眼神好像在说...{\r}\NI see that look in Mr Pitts' eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.68,0:25:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}十九世纪文学跟上商学院{\r}\Nlike 19th century literature has nothing to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.01,0:25:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}或者医学院没有关系{\r}\Ngoing to business school or medical school.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.02,0:25:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对吧 也许{\r}\NRight? Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.02,0:25:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}霍普金斯你可能也这么想 认为...{\r}\NMr Hopkins, you may agree with him, thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.19,0:25:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"对 我们应该老老实实学学...{\r}\N"Yes, we should simply study our Mr Pritchard...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.52,0:25:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}普里查特的理论格调韵律什么的{\r}\N"and learn our rhyme and metre and go quietly about the business...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.53,0:25:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}然后再去实现我们的其他理想"{\r}\Nof achieving other ambitions."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我有个秘密要告诉你 靠扰来{\r}\NI have a little secret for you. Huddle up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.70,0:25:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}靠扰来{\r}\NHuddle up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.54,0:25:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们读诗写诗 并不是因为它好玩{\r}\NWe don't read and write poetry because it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.05,0:25:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们读诗写诗是因为我们是人类的一分子{\r}\NWe read and write poetry because we are members of the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.89,0:25:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}而人类是充满激情的{\r}\NAnd the human race is filled with passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.72,0:25:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没错 医学 法律 商业 工程{\r}\NMedicine, law, business, engineering:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.39,0:25:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这些都是崇高的追求 足以支撑人的一生{\r}\Nthese are noble pursuits and necessary to sustain life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.65,0:25:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但诗歌...{\r}\NBut poetry,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.23,0:25:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}美丽 浪漫 爱情...{\r}\Nbeauty, romance, love...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.40,0:26:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这些才是我们生活的意义{\r}\Nthese are what we stay alive for.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.07,0:26:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}惠特曼曾写道{\r}\NTo quote from Whitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.99,0:26:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"自我 生命 这些问题总在不停出现"{\r}\N"O me, O life of the questions of these recurring.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.12,0:26:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"毫无信仰的人群川流不息"{\r}\N"Of the endless trains of the faithless.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.29,0:26:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"城市充斥着愚昧"{\r}\N"Of cities filled with the foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.30,0:26:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"生活在其中有什么意义 自我 生命"{\r}\N"What good amid these, O me, O life?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.67,0:26:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}答案是 因为你的存在{\r}\N"Answer: That you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.68,0:26:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因为你的存在{\r}\N"That life exists and identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.85,0:26:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因为伟大的戏剧在继续{\r}\N"That the powerful play goes on,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.35,0:26:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因为你可以奉献一首诗{\r}\Nand you may contribute a verse."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.02,0:26:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因为伟大的戏剧在继续{\r}\N"That the powerful play goes on,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.78,0:26:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因为你可以奉献一首诗{\r}\Nand you may contribute a verse."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.20,0:26:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你的诗是什么{\r}\NWhat will your verse be?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.33,0:26:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}为我们即将获得的一切{\r}\NFor what we are about to receive
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.21,0:26:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}愿主让我们心存感激{\r}\Nmay the Lord make us truly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.38,0:26:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}阿门{\r}\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.02,0:27:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你今天课上得很有意思 基丁先生{\r}\NQuite an interesting class you gave today, Mr Keating.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.86,0:27:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 抱歉吓了你一跳 麦卡利斯特先生  - 用不着道歉{\r}\N- Sorry if I shocked you, Mr McAllister.  - There's no need to apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.86,0:27:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}很有意思 虽然有些误导{\r}\NIt was very fascinating, misguided though it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.03,0:27:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是吗{\r}\NYou think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.03,0:27:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你鼓励他们成为艺术家是很冒险的 约翰{\r}\NYou take a big risk by encouraging them to become artists, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.37,0:27:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}等他们意识到他们不是伦勃朗 莎士比亚或者莫扎特{\r}\NWhen they realize that they're not Rembrandts, Shakespeares or Mozarts
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.20,0:27:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们会因此恨你的{\r}\Nthey'll hate you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.87,0:27:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不是让他们当艺术家 乔治 自由思想者{\r}\NWe're not talking artists, George. We're talking freethinkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.38,0:27:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}十七岁的自由思想者{\r}\NFreethinkers at 17?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.88,0:27:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}奇怪 没想到你这么悲观{\r}\NFunny, I never pegged you as a cynic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.22,0:27:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不是悲观{\r}\NNot a cynic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.01,0:27:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是现实{\r}\NA realist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.06,0:27:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们真能不满脑子胡思乱想{\r}\N"Show me the heart unfettered by foolish dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.23,0:27:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我也就不会悲观了{\r}\Nand I'll show you a happy man."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.52,0:27:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}只有在梦想中 人才能真正自由{\r}\N"But only in their dreams can men be truly free.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.23,0:27:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}从来如此也将永远如此{\r}\N'Twas always thus, and always thus will be."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.28,0:27:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}坦尼森{\r}\NTennyson?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.40,0:28:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 基丁{\r}\NNo. Keating.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.41,0:28:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}嘿 我在图书馆找到了他的记录{\r}\NHey, I found his senior annual in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.08,0:28:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}听好 足球队队长{\r}\NListen to this. Captain of the soccer team.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.21,0:28:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}校史年鉴编辑 考入剑桥大学{\r}\NEditor of the school annual. Cambridge bound.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.21,0:28:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}性格温和 死亡诗人俱乐部成员{\r}\NThigh man and the Dead Poets Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.47,0:28:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}充满幻想 敢做敢为{\r}\N"Man Most Likely To Do Anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.26,0:28:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}性格温和 他能把人吓死{\r}\NThigh man? Mr "K" was a hell-raiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.72,0:28:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}什么叫死亡诗人俱乐部{\r}\NWhat's the Dead Poets Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.52,0:28:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 不知道  - 年鉴上有照片吗{\r}\N- I don't know.  - Is there a picture in the annual?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.52,0:28:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 没有 这事别再提了  - 那边那个{\r}\N- Nothing. No other mention of it.  - That boy there,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.52,0:28:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}午饭后来见我{\r}\Nsee me after lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.03,0:28:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}基丁老师{\r}\NMr Keating?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.03,0:28:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}基丁老师{\r}\NMr Keating?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.82,0:28:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}先生{\r}\NSir?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.45,0:28:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 说点什么  - 哦 船长 我的船长{\r}\N- Say something.  - O Captain, my Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.29,0:28:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们好{\r}\NGentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.87,0:28:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们刚看到了你的记录{\r}\NWe were just looking in your old annual.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.54,0:28:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}哦 天哪{\r}\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.92,0:28:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 那不是我{\r}\NNo, that's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.38,0:29:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}斯坦利・威尔逊{\r}\NStanley "The Tool" Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.85,0:29:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 天哪  - 什么是死亡诗人俱乐部{\r}\N- God.  - What was the Dead Poets Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.86,0:29:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}现在的学校不会认为那是个什么好组织{\r}\NI doubt the present administration would look too favourably upon that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.48,0:29:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}为什么 那到底是什么{\r}\NWhy? What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.99,0:29:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 各位 你们能保密吗  - 当然{\r}\N- Gentlemen, can you keep a secret?  - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.50,0:29:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"死亡诗人致力于吸取生命的精华"{\r}\NThe Dead Poets were dedicated to sucking the marrow out of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.17,0:29:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是我们每次开会前都要引用的梭罗的一句话{\r}\NThat's a phrase from Thoreau we'd invoke at the beginning of every meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.51,0:29:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们经常在印地安山洞聚会{\r}\NYou see, we would gather at the old Indian cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.18,0:29:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}轮流朗诵梭罗 惠特曼 雪莱等诗人的作品{\r}\Nand take turns reading from Thoreau, Whitman, Shelley... the biggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.81,0:29:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}甚至我们自己的诗作{\r}\NEven some of our own verse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.68,0:29:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在那种痴迷的时刻 诗歌有着一种神奇的作用{\r}\NAnd in the enchantment of the moment, we'd let poetry work its magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.40,0:29:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你是说那也就是一帮坐在一起念诗的人{\r}\NYou mean it was a bunch of guys sitting around, reading poetry?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.69,0:29:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 奥弗斯特里特 并不像你想象的那样{\r}\NNo, Mr Overstreet. It wasn't just guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.69,0:29:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那并不是个很严密的组织 是一群浪漫主义者{\r}\NWe weren't a Greek organization. We were romantics.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.03,0:30:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们不仅仅是念诗 诗从我们舌间滑落 就像蜜糖{\r}\NWe didn't just read poetry, we let it drip from our tongues, like honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.16,0:30:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}情绪高涨 女人亢奋 灵魂驰骋{\r}\NSpirits soared, women swooned and gods were created, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.87,0:30:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这么度过一个夜晚也还不错{\r}\NNot a bad way to spend an evening, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.42,0:30:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}嗯{\r}\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.84,0:30:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢你 佩里 让我回想这么多过去的事{\r}\NThank you, Mr Perry, for this stroll down amnesia lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.71,0:30:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}烧了它{\r}\NBurn that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.84,0:30:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}尤其是我那张照片{\r}\NEspecially my picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.72,0:30:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}死亡诗人俱乐部{\r}\NDead Poets Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.23,0:30:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}什么{\r}\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.06,0:30:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我们今天晚上去  - 今晚{\r}\N- I say we go tonight.  - Tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.40,0:30:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 等一下  - 有谁参加{\r}\N- Wait a minute.  - Everybody in?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.57,0:30:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 他说的山洞在哪儿  - 就在河那边{\r}\N- Where's this cave he's talking about?  - It's beyond the stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.74,0:30:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我知道在哪儿  - 那远着呢{\r}\N- I know where it is.  - That's miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.24,0:30:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我看没什么意思  - 别去了{\r}\N- Sounds boring to me.  - Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.54,0:30:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}知道这会被扣掉多少学分吗 多尔顿{\r}\NYou know how many demerits we're talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.17,0:30:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那你就别去 行吗{\r}\NSo don't come. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.08,0:30:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 我只是说我们得小心{\r}\NLook, all I'm saying is that we have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.58,0:30:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 不能让人抓住  - 当然 真嗦{\r}\N- We can't get caught.  - No shit, Sherlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.79,0:30:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们干嘛呢 快点{\r}\NYou boys there! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.76,0:30:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 好了 谁参加  - 行了 尼尔 老师在看着呢{\r}\N- All right, who's in?  - Aw, come on, Neil. Hager's...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.93,0:31:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别管他了 谁参加{\r}\NForget Hager! No! Who's in?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.39,0:31:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我参加{\r}\NI'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.39,0:31:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我警告你们 快点{\r}\NI'm warning you! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.10,0:31:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我也参加{\r}\NMe too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.31,0:31:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我不知道 尼尔  - 什么 皮茨{\r}\N- I don't know, Neil.  - What? Pitts!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.77,0:31:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 皮茨 好啦  - 他功课太紧{\r}\N- Pittsie, come on.  - His grades are hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.77,0:31:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你可以帮他 米克斯{\r}\NYou can help him, Meeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.12,0:31:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这算什么 午夜学习小组{\r}\NWhat is this, a midnight study group?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.57,0:31:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}行啦 皮茨 参加吧 米克斯 你功课也紧吗{\r}\NForget it, Pitts. You're coming. Meeks, your grades hurting too?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.41,0:31:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 什么我都不怕  - 除了女孩{\r}\N- I'll try anything once.  - Except sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.82,0:31:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}只要小心点我就参加{\r}\NI'm in as long as we're careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.24,0:31:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你怎么样 诺克斯  - 我不知道 查理{\r}\N- What about you, Knox?  - I don't know, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.91,0:31:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好啦 诺克斯 这对你追克里丝有好处{\r}\NCome on, Knox. It'll help you get Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.08,0:31:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是吗 为什么{\r}\NYeah? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.08,0:31:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 女人亢奋  - 但她们为什么亢奋{\r}\N- Women swoon.  - But why do they swoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.92,0:31:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}查理 告诉我她们为什么亢奋{\r}\NCharlie, tell me why they swoon! Charlie!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.93,0:31:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}沿着小河走到瀑布{\r}\NOkay, follow the stream to the waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.47,0:31:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就在这儿 肯定就在那儿的河岸上{\r}\NIt's right there. It's got to be on the banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.47,0:31:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我不知道 我开始觉得这挺危险了{\r}\NI don't know. This is starting to sound dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.48,0:31:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 那你干嘛不呆在家里  - 什么 你疯了{\r}\N- Oh, well, why don't you stay home?  - Hey, you're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.98,0:31:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}看在上帝份上 别再嘀咕了 坐好{\r}\NFor God's sake, stop chattering and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.87,0:32:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 托德 你今晚去吗  - 不{\r}\N- Todd, are you coming tonight?  - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.66,0:32:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}为什么 托德 你当时也在 你听见他说的了{\r}\NWhy not? God, you were there. You heard Keating.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.83,0:32:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你就不想做点什么吗  - 想{\r}\N- Don't you want to do something about that?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.29,0:32:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 但是...  - 但是 但是什么{\r}\N- But...  - But? But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.38,0:32:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}基丁说每个人要轮流念诗{\r}\NKeating said that everybody took turns reading
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.22,0:32:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但我不想念诗{\r}\Nand I don't want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.05,0:32:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}念诗对你还真有什么问题吗{\r}\NGosh, you really have a problem with that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.39,0:32:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 没什么问题{\r}\NN... No, I don't have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.89,0:32:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}尼尔 我只是... 只是不想念 行吗{\r}\NNeil, I just... I don't want to do it, okay?
