Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.39,0:43:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 谢谢你的幽默{\r}\NNo! Thank you for playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.39,0:43:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我站到讲台上...{\r}\NI stand upon my desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.02,0:43:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是想提醒我自己我们必须时刻用不同的眼光来看待事物{\r}\Nto remind myself that we must constantly look at things in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.24,0:43:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}瞧 从这上面看世界 完全不同{\r}\NSee, the world looks very different from up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.58,0:43:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果不相信{\r}\NYou don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.70,0:43:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}可以自己来看 来吧{\r}\NCome see for yourselves. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.25,0:43:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}来吧 一旦你觉得自己懂得了什么{\r}\NCome on.Just when you think you know something,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.75,0:43:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就必须换一种角度来看{\r}\Nyou have to look at it in another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.75,0:43:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这可能显得很荒唐或者愚蠢{\r}\NEven though it may seem silly or wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.59,0:43:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但必须试一下{\r}\Nyou must try.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.59,0:43:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}同样 读书的时候不要只想作者怎么看{\r}\NNow when you read, don't just consider what the author thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.05,0:43:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}想想你怎么看{\r}\NConsider what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.06,0:43:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}同学们 你们必须努力寻找自己的声音{\r}\NBoys, you must strive to find your own voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.60,0:43:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因为你越迟开始寻找{\r}\NBecause the longer you wait to begin,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.60,0:43:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}找到的可能性就越小{\r}\Nthe less likely you are to find it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.07,0:43:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}梭罗说"大多数人都生活在平静的绝望中"{\r}\NThoreau said, "Most men lead lives of quiet desperation."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.44,0:44:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别陷入这种境地 冲出来{\r}\NDon't be resigned to that. Break out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.07,0:44:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别像老鼠逃跑似的 看看你的周围{\r}\NDon't just walk off the edge like lemmings. Look around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.45,0:44:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对了 就这样 布里斯克 谢谢{\r}\NThere you go, Mr Priske. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.25,0:44:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对极了{\r}\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.42,0:44:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}要敢于开拓新的天地{\r}\NDare to strike out and find new ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.75,0:44:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 除了写作文以外{\r}\NNow, in addition to your essays,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.42,0:44:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我希望你们每人写一首诗 自己的诗{\r}\NI would like you to compose a poem of your own, an original work.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.60,0:44:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这就对了{\r}\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.77,0:44:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}每个人星期一早晨都要在全班念自己的诗{\r}\NYou have to deliver it aloud, in front of the class on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.69,0:44:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}祝你们好运 各位{\r}\NBon chance, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.32,0:44:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安德森{\r}\NMr Anderson.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.78,0:44:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别以为我不知道这作业把你魂都吓没了{\r}\NDon't think I don't know this assignment scares the hell out of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.16,0:44:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}胆小鬼{\r}\Nyou mole.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.46,0:44:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}每两下用一次力{\r}\NTake a power train in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.63,0:45:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}三号 集中注意力{\r}\NThree, keep your eyes in the boat!
