Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.76,0:45:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我想干什么 就现在 我真正真正的梦想{\r}\NWhat I want to do right now. What's really, really inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.10,0:45:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- "仲夏夜之梦"  - 对{\r}\N- "A Midsummer Night's Dream."  - This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.43,0:45:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 这是什么  - 是一出戏 笨蛋{\r}\N- What is that?  - It's a play, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.40,0:45:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这我知道 但是... 这跟你有什么关系{\r}\NI know that. Wh... What does it have to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.02,0:45:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好吧 他们要在亨利会堂上演这出戏{\r}\NAll right, they're putting it on at Henley Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.11,0:45:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}欢迎试演 欢迎试演{\r}\NOpen tryouts. Open tryouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.53,0:46:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 所以  - 所以{\r}\N- Yeah, so?  - So!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.53,0:46:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我要演戏了{\r}\NI'm gonna act.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.53,0:46:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}演戏 演戏 我要当演员了{\r}\NYes! Yes! I'm gonna be an actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.70,0:46:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}很早以前我就想试一试{\r}\NEver since I can remember, I've wanted to try this!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.87,0:46:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}去年我还曾想参加暑期剧团试演{\r}\NI even tried to go to summer stock auditions last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.88,0:46:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}当然 我爸没让{\r}\Nbut, of course, my father wouldn't let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.04,0:46:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我平生第一次知道了我到底想做什么{\r}\NFor the first time in my whole life, I know what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.55,0:46:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}也是第一次 我决心要做成...{\r}\NAnd for the first time, I'm gonna do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.22,0:46:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不管我爸同不同意{\r}\Nwhether my father wants me to or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.22,0:46:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 卡匹迪恩  - 尼尔 尼尔 等一下{\r}\N- Carpe diem!  - Neil, Neil, hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.56,0:46:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果你爸不让 你怎么去演戏呢{\r}\NHow are you gonna be in a play if your father won't let you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.10,0:46:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我首先要争取到角色 然后再想这个问题{\r}\NFirst, I gotta get the part, then I can worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.90,0:46:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但如果他发现你都没跟他说一声就去参加试演{\r}\NBut won't he kill you if he finds out you went to an audition
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.79,0:46:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他还不杀了你{\r}\Nand didn't tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.40,0:46:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 不 不 照我看来{\r}\NNo, no, no. As far as I'm concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.03,0:46:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}根本用不着让他知道这件事{\r}\Nhe won't have to know about any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.44,0:46:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 这不可能  - 不 没什么不可能{\r}\N- Well, that's impossible.  - Bullshit. Nothing's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.99,0:46:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}听我说 你干嘛不打个电话问问他 也许他会同意{\r}\NWell, why don't you just call him and ask him and m-maybe he'll say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.74,0:46:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}简直笑话{\r}\NThat's a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.41,0:46:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果不问他 至少我没违抗他的意愿{\r}\NIf I don't ask him, at least I won't be disobeying him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.75,0:46:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是 但如果他以前就不同意...{\r}\NYeah, but if he said no before...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.22,0:46:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}天哪 托德 你站在谁一边{\r}\NJesus, Todd, whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.72,0:47:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我意思是现在连角色还没弄到{\r}\NI mean, I haven't even gotten the part yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.06,0:47:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我就不能先在脑子里过过瘾{\r}\NCan't I even enjoy the idea for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.41,0:47:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你参加下午的聚会吗  - 我不知道 也许会{\r}\N- You're coming to the meeting?  - I don't know. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.91,0:47:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}基丁老师的话对你狗屁不算 是吗 托德{\r}\NNothing Mr Keating has to say means shit to you, does it, Todd?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.42,0:47:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 这... 这是什么意思  - 你是俱乐部成员{\r}\N- Wh... What is that supposed to mean?  - You're in the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.75,0:47:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是成员就意味着充满激情{\r}\NBeing in the club means being stirred up by things.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.21,0:47:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但你看上去像一潭死水{\r}\NYou look about as stirred up as a cesspool.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.21,0:47:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你要我退出  - 我要你参与{\r}\N- So you want me out?  - No, I want you in!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.76,0:47:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但参与意味着你得做点事情 不是光嘴上说{\r}\NBut being in means you gotta do something, not just say you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.72,0:47:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}听我说 尼尔 我是说谢谢你的关心{\r}\NListen, Neil, I mean, I appreciate this concern,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.93,0:47:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但是我和你不一样 对不对{\r}\Nbut I'm not like you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.43,0:47:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你... 你... 你说话有人听{\r}\NYou... You... You say things and people listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.77,0:47:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我... 我... 我不一样{\r}\NI... I... I'm not like that.
