Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.17,0:50:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}皮茨 让你的名字更响亮{\r}\NMr Pitts... rise above your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.17,0:50:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你把这些发下去 每人一张{\r}\NI want you to hand these out to the boys, one a piece.
