Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.60,0:51:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"与逆境不屈地抗争 以无畏的气势面对敌人"{\r}\N"Oh, to struggle against great odds, to meet enemies undaunted"!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.77,0:51:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 开始{\r}\NNow go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.19,0:51:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好的 下一个{\r}\NYes! Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.44,0:51:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"做一个世界的水手 游遍所有的港口"{\r}\N"To be a sailor of the world bound for all ports."
