Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.41,0:51:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"走上绞刑台"{\r}\N"To mount the scaffolds.
