Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.80,0:51:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}来吧 米克斯 听着音乐{\r}\NCome on, Meeks! Listen to the music!
