Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.31,0:51:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 飘飘荡荡 滚滚向前  - 下一个{\r}\N- roll on, float on!"  - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.35,0:51:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}让生活从此变成一首欢乐的诗{\r}\N"Oh, to have life henceforth, the poem of new joys."
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.99,0:52:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}快点 查理 让它充满你的灵魂{\r}\NCome on, Charlie, let it fill your soul.
