Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.42,0:52:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 祝贺你 尼尔  - 很适合你 很适合你{\r}\N- Congratulations.  - Good for you! Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.26,0:52:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 好了{\r}\NOkay, okay, okay, okay.
