Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.92,0:54:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}祝贺你 霍普金斯{\r}\NCongratulations, Mr Hopkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.59,0:54:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}按照普里查特的评分方法{\r}\NYours is the first poem to ever have a negative
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.01,0:54:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你的诗是第一首得负分的{\r}\Nscore on the Pritchard scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.30,0:54:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们不是在笑你 是在恭喜你{\r}\NWe're not laughing at you, we're laughing near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.93,0:54:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我不在乎你的诗主题简单{\r}\NI don't mind that your poem had a simple theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.60,0:54:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有时候最漂亮的诗主题也很简单{\r}\NSometimes the most beautiful poetry can be about simple things,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.93,0:54:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}像一只猫 一朵花 一场雨{\r}\Nlike a cat or a flower or rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.06,0:55:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}知道吗 只要有新意 什么东西都可以写出诗来{\r}\NYou see, poetry can come from anything with the stuff of revelation in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.36,0:55:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}只是不要让你的诗太俗套{\r}\NJust don't let your poems be ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.61,0:55:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 谁下一位{\r}\NNow, who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.57,0:55:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安德森先生 你在那儿坐立不安{\r}\NMr Anderson, I see you sitting there in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.45,0:55:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}来吧 托德 站起来 让我们结束你的痛苦吧{\r}\NCome on, Todd, step up. Let's put you out of your misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.33,0:55:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我... 我没做 我没写诗{\r}\NI... I didn't do it. I didn't write a poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.30,0:55:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安德森认为自己内心的想法全都没有价值 都让人笑话{\r}\NMr Anderson thinks everything inside of him is worthless and embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.26,0:55:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是这样吗 托德 这是你最担心的{\r}\NIsn't that right, Todd? Isn't that your worst fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.93,0:55:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那么 你错了 我觉得你内心有些东西...{\r}\NWell, I think you're wrong. I think you have something inside of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.60,0:55:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是很有价值的{\r}\Nthat is worth a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.69,0:55:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我喊出...{\r}\N"I sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.32,0:55:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我野性的...{\r}\N"my barbaric...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.70,0:55:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}狂叫{\r}\N"yawp...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.41,0:55:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}站在...{\r}\N"over the rooftops...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.75,0:56:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}世界的屋脊上{\r}\Nof the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.50,0:56:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}又是惠特曼的诗{\r}\NUncle Walt, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.34,0:56:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 可能你们有些不知道 咆哮是一种大声的叫喊{\r}\NNow, for those of you who don't know, a yawp is a loud cry or yell.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.93,0:56:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 托德 你给我们演示一下什么叫野性的咆哮{\r}\NNow, Todd, I would like you to give us a demonstration of a barbaric yawp.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.31,0:56:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}行了 你不会坐着咆哮{\r}\NCome on, you can't yawp sitting down.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.69,0:56:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}来吧 快点上去{\r}\NLet's go. Come on, up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.98,0:56:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 做好咆哮的姿势{\r}\NGot to get in yawping stance.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.07,0:56:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 咆哮  - 不仅仅是咆哮 野性的咆哮{\r}\N- A... A yawp?  - Not just a yawp. A barbaric yawp.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.86,0:56:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 好吧 咆哮  - 不行 大声点{\r}\N- Right. Yawp.  - Come on. Louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.45,0:56:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 咆哮  - 那是老鼠叫 来吧 大声点{\r}\N- Yawp.  - That's a mouse. Come on, louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.58,0:56:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 咆哮  - 天哪 叫得像个男人{\r}\N- Yawp.  - Oh, good God, boy, yell like a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.58,0:56:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 咆哮  - 这就对了{\r}\N- Yawp!  - There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.08,0:56:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你瞧 你身上到底也有野性{\r}\NYou see, you have a barbarian in you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.67,0:56:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}还不能这么就走 那是张惠特曼的照片{\r}\NYou don't get away that easy. There's a picture of Uncle Walt up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.21,0:56:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他让你想起谁 别想 回答 快点{\r}\NWhat does he remind you of? Don't think, answer. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.22,0:56:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 一个... 一个疯子  - 什么样的疯子{\r}\N- A m-m-m-madman.  - What kind of madman?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.55,0:56:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 不用想 只管回答  - 一个疯狂的疯子{\r}\N- Don't think about it, just answer.  - A cr-crazy madman.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.56,0:56:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你可以答得更好 解放你的思想 发挥你的想象力{\r}\NNo, you can do better than that. Free up your mind. Use your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.43,0:56:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说出第一个跳进你脑子的东西 哪怕荒唐透顶{\r}\NSay the first thing that pops into your head, even if it's total gibberish.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.06,0:57:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一... 一个牙齿流汗的疯子{\r}\NA-A-A sweaty-toothed madman.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.23,0:57:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我的天哪 你还是有诗人气质嘛{\r}\NGood God, boy, there's a poet in you after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.94,0:57:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 闭上眼睛 闭上眼睛{\r}\NThere. Close your eyes. Close your eyes. Close them.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.82,0:57:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 说你看到了什么{\r}\NNow, describe what you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.99,0:57:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我闭上了眼睛...  - 还有呢{\r}\N- Uh, I... I close my eyes...  - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.78,0:57:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 他的形像在我眼前见  - 一个牙齿流汗的疯子{\r}\N- uh, and his image floats beside me.  - A sweaty-toothed madman.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.54,0:57:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一个牙齿流汗的疯子瞪得我心嘭嘭直跳{\r}\NA sweaty-toothed madman with a stare that pounds my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.33,0:57:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}哦 好极了{\r}\NOh, that's excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.83,0:57:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}让他动起来 让他做点什么{\r}\NNow, give him action, make him do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.84,0:57:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他... 他伸出手掐我脖子{\r}\NHis hands reach out and choke me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.15,0:57:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对了 好极了 好极了{\r}\NThat's it. Wonderful. Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.38,0:57:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 他一直在念叨  - 念叨什么{\r}\N- And all the time he's mumbling.  - What's he mumbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.38,0:57:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 念叨真理  - 对{\r}\N- Mumbling truth.  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.38,0:57:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}真理就像一床总让你双脚冰凉的毯子{\r}\NTruth is like a blanket that always leaves your feet cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.89,0:57:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别管他们 继续说毯子 继续说下去{\r}\NForget them. Forget them. Stay with the blanket. Tell me about that blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.93,0:57:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你怎么扯 怎么拽 总也不够{\r}\NY-Y-You push it, stretch it, it'll never be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.44,0:57:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}踢也好 打也好 它总盖不住我们{\r}\NYou kick at it, beat it, it'll never cover any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.60,0:57:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}从我们哭着降生到我们奄奄一息{\r}\NFrom the moment we enter crying to the moment we leave dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.03,0:57:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}它只会盖住你的脸 不管你如何痛哭 如何叫喊{\r}\Nit'll just cover your face as you wail and cry and scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.46,0:58:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不要忘记了{\r}\NDon't you forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.56,0:59:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你太嫩了 皮茨{\r}\NThat a boy, Pittsie.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.03,0:59:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 吸气 深一点  - 我爸收集了很多烟斗{\r}\N- Inhale, deeply.  - My dad collects pipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.36,0:59:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 真的  - 我爸至少有三十个{\r}\N- Really?  - He must have 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.70,0:59:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你家里收集烟斗 真有意思{\r}\NYour parents collect pipes? Oh, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.45,0:59:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}诺克斯 来一口{\r}\NCome on, Knox.Join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.08,0:59:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对 诺克斯 我们是政府派来的{\r}\NYeah, Knox, we're from the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.70,0:59:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}来帮你的 有什么事吗{\r}\NWe're here to help. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.71,0:59:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 是克里丝  - 是克里丝的照片 看{\r}\N- It's Chris!  - Here's a picture of Chris for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.08,0:59:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 把它放在你的烟管里抽了它  - 这没意思{\r}\N- Put that in your pipe and smoke it.  - It's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.09,0:59:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别闹了 抽你们的烟吧{\r}\NKnock it off. Smoke your pipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.59,0:59:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 尼尔  - 朋友们 同学们 校友们{\r}\N- Neil.  - Friends, scholars, Welton men.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.39,0:59:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那是什么 尼尔{\r}\NWhat is that, Neil?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.68,0:59:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 是盏灯 笨蛋  - 不 这是山洞之神{\r}\N- Duh, it's a lamp, Meeks.  - No, this is the god of the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.89,0:59:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}山洞之神{\r}\NThe god of the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.57,0:59:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 查理 你在干什么  - 开始今天的会议日程吧{\r}\N- Charlie, what are you doing?  - What do you say we start this meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.90,0:59:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 等等 我需要灯 谁带灯了  - 你带耳塞了吗{\r}\N- I need a light. Who's got a light?  - Anybody bring earplugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.11,0:59:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}各位{\r}\NGentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.49,0:59:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}查尔斯・多尔顿的诗人音乐{\r}\N"Poetrusic" by Charles Dalton.
