Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.09,1:16:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你是第一个想被学校开除的人 你错了{\r}\Nthat you're the first to try to get thrown out of this school, think again.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.14,1:16:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}其他人也有过这种想法{\r}\NOthers have had similar notions
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.09,1:16:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但他们想错了 就像你一样{\r}\Nand have failed just as surely as you will fail.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.31,1:17:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}摆好姿势{\r}\NAssume the position.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.99,1:17:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}大声数 多尔顿{\r}\NCount aloud, Mr Dalton.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.83,1:17:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一{\r}\NOne.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.00,1:17:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}二{\r}\NTwo.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.18,1:17:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}三{\r}\NThree.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.89,1:17:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}四{\r}\NFour.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.56,1:17:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}五{\r}\NFive.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.02,1:17:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}什么叫死亡诗人俱乐部 告诉我名字{\r}\NWhat is this Dead Poets Society? I want names.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.97,1:18:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 被开除了  - 不{\r}\N- You kicked out?  - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.30,1:18:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那怎么回事{\r}\NSo what happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.14,1:18:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}让我把所有人供出来 向全校道歉{\r}\NI'm to turn everybody in, apologise to the school,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.81,1:18:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}然后大家都没事{\r}\Nand all will be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.98,1:18:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那你准备怎么办{\r}\NSo what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.28,1:18:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 查理  - 见鬼 尼尔{\r}\N- Charlie...  - Damn it, Neil,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.65,1:18:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我叫纽旺达{\r}\Nthe name is Nuwanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.16,1:18:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对不起 能谈谈吗 基丁老师{\r}\NExcuse me. May we have a word, Mr Keating?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.67,1:18:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}可以{\r}\NCertainly.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.09,1:18:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是我上课的第一间教室 你知道吗{\r}\NThis was my first classroom, John. Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.26,1:18:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}第一张讲台{\r}\NMy first desk.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.60,1:18:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不知道你还教过课 诺兰先生{\r}\NI didn't know you taught, Mr Nolan.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.10,1:19:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}教英语 比你早多了{\r}\NEnglish. Long before your time.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.61,1:19:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不教还真舍不得 说老实话{\r}\NIt was hard giving it up, I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.28,1:19:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我听传言说{\r}\NI'm hearing rumours
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.76,1:19:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你在你班上用的一些非正统的教学方法{\r}\Nabout some unorthodox teaching methods in your classroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.45,1:19:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我不是说这跟那个叫多尔顿的学生的错误有关{\r}\NI'm not saying they've had anything to do with the Dalton boy's outburst,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.79,1:19:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但我想我用不着提醒你{\r}\Nbut I don't think I have to warn you boys
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.89,1:19:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他这种年龄的孩子很容易受人影响{\r}\Nhis age are very impressionable.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.63,1:19:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你的惩罚对他很有影响 我肯定{\r}\NWell, your reprimand made quite an impression, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.63,1:19:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 那天在院子里是怎么回事  - 院子{\r}\N- What was going on in the courtyard the other day?  - Courtyard?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.81,1:19:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 孩子们一起走 一起拍手  - 那个...{\r}\N- Boys marching, clapping in unison.  - Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.97,1:19:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那是为了证明一个观点 顺从的危险{\r}\NThat was an exercise to prove a point: dangers of conformity.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.19,1:19:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}约翰 这儿的课程是固定的 已经过检验并很有效{\r}\NWell, John, the curriculum here is set. It's proven. It works.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.11,1:19:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果你有疑问 也不该随随便便乱改{\r}\NIf you question it, what's to prevent them from doing the same?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.78,1:19:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我始终认为教育的根本在于学会自我思考{\r}\NI always thought the idea of education was to learn to think for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.28,1:19:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在他们这种年纪 开玩笑{\r}\NAt these boys' age? Not on your life!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.99,1:19:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}传统 纪律{\r}\NTradition, John. Discipline.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.12,1:19:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}送他们上大学 其余的就不用管了{\r}\NPrepare them for college, and the rest will take care of itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.96,1:20:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他当时正朝我左边绕过来{\r}\NHe starts walking around towards my left.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.39,1:20:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}摆好姿势 多尔顿 也就是说...{\r}\N'Assume the position, Mr Dalton, " which means...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.10,1:20:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们好 各位{\r}\NAll right, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.31,1:20:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 基丁老师  - 多尔顿{\r}\N- Mr Keating.  - Mr Dalton.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.48,1:20:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你今天的表演很拙劣{\r}\NThat was a pretty lame stunt you pulled today.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.82,1:20:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你跟诺兰老师站一边{\r}\NYou're siding with Mr Nolan?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.82,1:20:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那卡匹迪恩和吸取生命中所有精华{\r}\NWhat about carpe diem and sucking all the marrow...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.82,1:20:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 是怎么回事  - 吸取生命中所有精华...{\r}\N- out of life and all that?  - Sucking the marrow out of life...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.66,1:20:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不是叫你胡来{\r}\Ndoesn't mean choking on the bone.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.74,1:20:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有时候要大胆 有时候要小心{\r}\NThere is a time for daring, and there is a time for caution.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.16,1:20:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一个聪明人知道什么时候该怎么做{\r}\NAnd a wise man understands which is called for.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.67,1:20:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我还以为你会喜欢呢{\r}\NBut I thought you'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.96,1:20:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不{\r}\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.96,1:20:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在我看来 被学校开除不是勇敢 是愚蠢{\r}\NYou being expelled from school is not daring to me. It's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.01,1:20:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因为你会失去很多大好的机会{\r}\N'Cause you'll miss some golden opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.55,1:20:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是吗 比方说{\r}\NYeah? Like what?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.09,1:20:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}比方 不说别的 听我的课的机会{\r}\NLike, if nothing else, the opportunity to attend my classes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.06,1:21:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}明白了 英雄{\r}\NGot it, ace?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.52,1:21:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}唉 船长{\r}\NAye, aye, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.36,1:21:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}做事用点脑子{\r}\NKeep your head about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.90,1:21:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们也都一样{\r}\NThat goes for the lot of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.78,1:21:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 是 船长  - 是 船长{\r}\N- Yes, Captain.  - Yes, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.78,1:21:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}上帝来电话{\r}\NPhone call from God.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.74,1:21:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果由受话人付款就称得上勇敢了{\r}\NIf it'd been collect, it would have been daring.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.29,1:21:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 好吧 继续  - 不{\r}\N- All right. Go on, boy.  - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.56,1:21:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们练习一遍 好吗 开始{\r}\NWe're trying to rehearse, okay? Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.31,1:21:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我有个想法 所以请听我说 赫米亚{\r}\NA good persuasion, therefore hear me, Hermia.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.48,1:21:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我感觉不到任何的激情 我没有听到任何一句有激情的话{\r}\NWait, wait. The excitement. I don't hear any excitement about this play.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.44,1:21:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}拉住她的手 领她下来{\r}\NNow take her hand, bring her downstage...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.94,1:21:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}然后说 "美丽 温柔的赫米亚"{\r}\Nand stop and "Fair, gentle Hermia."
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.03,1:21:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}行吗 试一下{\r}\NOkay? Try again.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.24,1:21:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}晚饭吃什么{\r}\NWhat's for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.24,1:21:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 空心粉和肉丸子  - 吃饭啦{\r}\N- Spaghetti and meatballs!  - Food!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.62,1:22:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}给我留点儿{\r}\NSave some for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.46,1:22:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}快走 小仙女 奥伯伦来了{\r}\N"But, room, fairy! Here comes Oberon."
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.30,1:22:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 爸爸  - 尼尔{\r}\N- Father.  - Neil.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.14,1:22:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}等一下 您先别说...{\r}\NWait a minute. Before you say anything,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.39,1:22:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 请听我解释...  - 你居然敢跟我顶嘴{\r}\N- please let me ex...  - Don't you dare talk back to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.23,1:22:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你浪费时间去演什么破戏...{\r}\NIt's bad enough that you've wasted your time...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.48,1:22:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}已经够意思了{\r}\Nwith this, this absurd acting business,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.03,1:22:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但你居然故意欺骗我{\r}\Nbut you deliberately deceived me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.32,1:22:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你以为能逃脱得了{\r}\NHow... How... How did you expect to get away with this?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.99,1:22:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}回答我{\r}\NAnswer me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.16,1:22:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谁唆使你干的{\r}\NWho put you up to it?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.29,1:22:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 是那个新来的老师 叫基丁的  - 不{\r}\N- Was it this new man? Keating?  - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.63,1:22:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没人唆使 我只是想给你个惊喜{\r}\NNobody p... I thought I'd surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.35,1:22:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我每门课都得了A{\r}\NI've gotten all A's in every class.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.71,1:22:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你真以为我发现不了{\r}\NDid you really think I wasn't going to find out?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.05,1:22:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}马克斯夫人说 "我侄女和你儿子在演一出戏"{\r}\N"Oh, my niece is in a play with your son," says Mrs Marks.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.10,1:22:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"不 不 不" 我说{\r}\N"No, no, no," I say.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.76,1:22:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"你肯定搞错了 我儿子没在演戏"{\r}\N"You must be mistaken. My son's not in a play."
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.02,1:22:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你让我成了个骗子 尼尔{\r}\NYou made a liar out of me, Neil!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.02,1:23:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 明天你去找他们 告诉他们你不演了{\r}\NNow, tomorrow, you go to them and you tell them that you're quitting.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.57,1:23:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 不行{\r}\NNo, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.57,1:23:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我演的是主角 明天晚上就上演{\r}\NI have the main part. The performance is tomorrow night!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.78,1:23:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就是世界明天晚上毁灭 我也不管{\r}\NI don't care if the world comes to an end tomorrow night,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.87,1:23:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那戏你不能去演{\r}\Nyou are through with that play!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.12,1:23:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}明白了吗{\r}\NIs that clear?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.12,1:23:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}明白了吗{\r}\NIs that clear?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.54,1:23:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}明白了{\r}\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.51,1:23:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我付出了很大的牺牲才把你弄到这儿来{\r}\NI made a great many sacrifices to get you here, Neil,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.27,1:23:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你不能让我失望{\r}\Nand you will not let me down.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.56,1:23:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}知道{\r}\NNo, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.09,1:24:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}门开着{\r}\NIt's open.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.77,1:24:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}尼尔 怎么啦{\r}\NNeil, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.77,1:24:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我能和你谈谈吗  - 当然 坐吧{\r}\N- Can I speak to you a minute?  - Certainly. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.61,1:24:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 对不起 给你  - 很抱歉{\r}\N- I'm sorry. Here.  - Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.32,1:24:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 喝杯茶  - 茶 好的{\r}\N- Get you some tea?  - Tea? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.95,1:24:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 要加点奶或者糖吗  - 不用 谢谢{\r}\N- Want some milk or sugar in that?  - No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.37,1:24:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们给你的房间够小的{\r}\NGosh, they don't give you much room around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.62,1:24:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}修行生活的一部分{\r}\NIt's part of the monastic oath.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.54,1:24:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们不想让世俗的东西让我分神{\r}\NThey don't want worldly things distracting me from my teaching.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.97,1:24:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 她很漂亮  - 她也在伦敦{\r}\N- She's pretty.  - She's also in London.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.97,1:24:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}所以有些不方便{\r}\NMakes it a little difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.14,1:24:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你怎么忍受得了  - 忍受什么{\r}\N- How do you stand it?  - Stand what?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.23,1:24:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你哪儿都可以去 什么都可以做{\r}\NYou can go anywhere. You can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.63,1:24:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你怎么能忍受呆在这儿呢{\r}\NHow can you stand being here?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.64,1:25:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因为我喜欢教书 我不想去其他地方{\r}\NBecause I love teaching. I don't want to be anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.11,1:25:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 怎么了  - 我刚和我父亲谈过{\r}\N- What's up?  - I just talked to my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.20,1:25:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他要我退出那场戏的演出{\r}\NHe's making me quit the play at Henley Hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.70,1:25:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但演戏对我很重要{\r}\NBut acting is everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.96,1:25:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我是说... 但他不知道...{\r}\NI mean... But he doesn't know. He...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.17,1:25:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我明白他的意思 我们家不富裕{\r}\NI can see his point. We're not a rich family
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.09,1:25:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不像查理 我是说...{\r}\Nlike Charlie's. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.26,1:25:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但他想替我安排我的将来{\r}\NBut he's planning the rest of my life for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.43,1:25:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他从来不问我想什么{\r}\NAnd he... he's never asked me what I want.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.93,1:25:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你跟你父亲说过你刚跟我说的话吗{\r}\NHave you ever told your father what you just told me?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.89,1:25:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你对戏剧的热爱 告诉过他吗{\r}\NAbout your passion for acting? Have you showed him that?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.69,1:25:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我做不到  - 为什么{\r}\N- I can't.  - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.86,1:25:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我不能这么跟他说话{\r}\NI can't talk to him this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.86,1:25:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那你在他面前也在表演{\r}\NThen you're acting for him too.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.61,1:25:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}演一个听话的儿子的角色{\r}\NYou're playing the part of the dutiful son.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.91,1:25:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我知道这听起来好像不可能 但你必须跟他谈{\r}\NI know this sounds impossible, but you have to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.91,1:25:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}必须让他明白你是什么人 你的心在哪儿{\r}\NYou have to show him who you are, what your heart is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.70,1:25:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我知道他会说什么{\r}\NI know what he'll say.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.29,1:25:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他会说演戏是一时心血来潮 我不要再想了{\r}\NHe'll tell me that acting's a whim and I should forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.87,1:26:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说他们就指望我了{\r}\NThey're counting on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.46,1:26:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}告诉我不要再想这些了 为了我自己好{\r}\NHe'll just tell me to put it out of my mind for my own good.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.88,1:26:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你又不是个雇来的仆人{\r}\NYou are not an indentured servant.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.80,1:26:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那不是你心血来潮{\r}\NIt's not a whim for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.68,1:26:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}用你的坚定和激情向他证明这一点{\r}\NYou prove it to him by your conviction and your passion.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.60,1:26:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}让他明白这一点 如果他还不相信你...{\r}\NYou show him that, and if he still doesn't believe you...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.10,1:26:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那时候你也毕业了 想干什么都可以了{\r}\NWell, by then, you'll be out of school, and you can do anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.35,1:26:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不{\r}\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.52,1:26:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那这戏怎么办 明晚就要上演{\r}\NWhat about the play? The show's tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.78,1:26:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那你就得在明晚之前跟他谈{\r}\NThen you have to talk to him before tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.41,1:26:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我...{\r}\NI...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.45,1:26:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我有没有容易点儿的办法  - 没有{\r}\N- Isn't there an easier way?  - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.79,1:26:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我走投无路了{\r}\NI'm trapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.71,1:26:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 你不是{\r}\NNo, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.28,1:27:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}克里丝{\r}\NChris!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.95,1:27:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}克里丝・诺埃尔 你知道她在哪儿吗{\r}\NChris! Chris Noel. Do you know where she is?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.70,1:27:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 好像在111号房间  - 谢谢{\r}\N- Um, I think she's in Room 111.  - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.58,1:27:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我知道了{\r}\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.47,1:27:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对不起 克里斯...{\r}\NExcuse me. Chris...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.51,1:27:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}诺克斯 你到这儿来干嘛{\r}\NKnox, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.47,1:27:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}来为那晚的事道歉{\r}\NI came to apologize for the other night.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.47,1:27:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这送给你 我还给你写了首诗{\r}\NI brought you these and a poem I wrote for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.15,1:27:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}诺克斯 你不知道如果切特发现你在这儿{\r}\NKnox, don't you know that if Chet finds you here,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.18,1:27:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他会杀了你吗{\r}\Nhe'll kill you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.86,1:27:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我不管 我爱你 克里丝  - 诺克斯 你疯了{\r}\N- I don't care. I love you, Chris.  - Knox, you're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.82,1:27:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}听我说 我表现得像个傻瓜 我知道{\r}\NLook, I acted like a jerk, and I know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.53,1:27:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 请你接受 求你了  - 不 不 我... 我不能{\r}\N- Please accept these. Please.  - No. No, I... I can't.
