Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.60,1:33:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你说对了{\r}\NThou speak'st aright.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.61,1:33:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我就是那个快乐的夜游人{\r}\NI am that merry wanderer of the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.86,1:33:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我跟奥伯伦开玩笑逗他开心{\r}\NI jest to Oberon and make him smile...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.78,1:33:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我装成一匹高大的马{\r}\Nwhen I a fat and bean-fed horse beguile.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.57,1:33:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}却学小母马叫{\r}\NNeighing in the likeness of a filly foal.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.74,1:33:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有时候我躲在大酒杯里{\r}\NSometime lurk I in a gossip's bowl...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.50,1:34:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}装成一只烤熟的螃蟹{\r}\Nin very likeness of a roasted crab.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.21,1:34:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她端起酒杯 我就窜到她嘴上{\r}\NAnd when she drink, against her lips I bob...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.29,1:34:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}吓得她把酒灌进脖子里{\r}\Nand on her withered dewlap pour the ale.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.96,1:34:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 闹她个大笑话  - 演得好 演得真好{\r}\N- The wisest aunt telling the saddest tale.  - He's good. He's really good.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.13,1:34:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有时候我装成一条三足凳{\r}\NSometime for three-foot stool mistaketh me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.89,1:34:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}然后从她屁股底下溜走 弄得她一屁股摔倒{\r}\NThen slip I from her bum, down topples she and "Tailor" cries...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.64,1:34:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不停地咳嗽{\r}\Nand falls into a cough.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.64,1:34:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}然后所有人都捧腹大笑{\r}\NAnd then the whole quire hold their hips and laugh...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.56,1:34:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}笑得前仰后合{\r}\Nand waxen in their mirth nee-e-e-eze...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.90,1:34:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说...{\r}\Nand swear.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.03,1:34:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}从没有过这么开心的时候{\r}\NA merrier hour was never wasted there.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.24,1:34:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}快走 小仙女{\r}\NBut, room, fairy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.57,1:34:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是奥伯伦 他来了{\r}\NHere comes Oberon.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.53,1:34:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}还有小妞 来得真不是时候{\r}\NAnd here, my mistress. Would that he were gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.50,1:34:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}只要能躺在你身边 再好的卧室也不能让我离开{\r}\NThen by your side, no bed-room me deny.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.92,1:34:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我没有说谎 赫米亚{\r}\NFor lying so, Hermia, I do not lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.00,1:34:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我没有说你说谎{\r}\NLysander riddles very prettily. Much beshrew my manners...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.13,1:34:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那样的话我也太失敬爱和礼貌了{\r}\Nand my pride if Hermia meant to say Lysander lied.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.35,1:34:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不过 我的朋友 出于敬爱和礼节{\r}\NBut, gentle friend, for love and courtesy...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.47,1:34:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}请躺远一点 按礼敬的标准{\r}\Nlie further off, in human modesty,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.69,1:35:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这样的距离才适合一对品行纯洁的单身男子和姑娘{\r}\Nsuch separation as may well be said becomes a virtuous bachelor and maid.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.15,1:35:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}晚安 亲爱的朋友 愿你的爱终身不渝{\r}\NGood night, sweet friend. Thy love ne'er alter 'til thy sweet life end.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.32,1:35:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}阿门 愿你的祈祷成真{\r}\NAmen. Amen to that fair prayer, say I.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.20,1:35:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我结束了忠诚也就结束了生命{\r}\NAnd then end life when I end loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.57,1:35:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}尼尔 该你上了 尼尔{\r}\NNeil. That's your cue, Neil.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.78,1:35:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}快点 尼尔 你的帽子 走吧{\r}\NCome on, Neil. Here's your crown. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.90,1:36:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果我们的出现冒犯了各位...{\r}\NIf we shadows have offended...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.07,1:36:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}请原谅我们的过失{\r}\Nthink but this and all is mended.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.70,1:36:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就当我们出现的时候 你们在这儿睡了一觉{\r}\NThat you have but slumber'd here while these visions did appear.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.49,1:36:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这场小小的闹剧只不过是一场梦境{\r}\NAnd this weak and idle theme, no more yielding but a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.00,1:36:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}各位 请不要过于怪罪{\r}\NGentles, do not reprehend.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.79,1:36:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果允许 我们会悔过{\r}\NIf you pardon, we will mend.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.04,1:36:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我是一个诚实的小鬼 如果我们有幸逃过惩罚{\r}\NAnd as I am an honest Puck, if we have unearned luck,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.76,1:36:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们会很快改过自新{\r}\Nnow to 'scape the serpent's tongue,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.22,1:36:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不然你就叫我是个骗子{\r}\Nwe will make amends ere long; else the Puck a liar call.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.17,1:36:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好了 祝各位晚安{\r}\NSo, good night unto you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.72,1:37:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}请把手伸给我 如果我们是朋友{\r}\NGive me your hands if we be friends,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.97,1:37:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}再次请求你们的宽怨{\r}\Nand Robin shall restore amends.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.88,1:37:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}卡匹迪恩{\r}\NYawp! Carpe diem!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.53,1:38:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}太棒了{\r}\NThat was great!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.95,1:38:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我是尼尔的父亲 我想见见他 行吗{\r}\NExcuse me. I'm Neil's father. I'd like to see him, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.59,1:38:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}尼尔 你爸找你{\r}\NNeil, your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.92,1:38:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你认为怎样  - 你的表演真实太精彩了{\r}\N- What did you think?  - You were all just wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.74,1:38:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对不起 请让一下{\r}\NExcuse me, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.74,1:38:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 对不起 请让一下  - 尼尔 过来{\r}\N- Excuse me. Excuse me.  - Neil! Back here! Neil!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.66,1:38:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}尼尔 尼尔 太棒了 回去吧 尼尔{\r}\NNeil, Neil, you were great! Come back, Neil.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.79,1:38:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 不行 伙计们  - 尼尔{\r}\N- I can't, guys.  - Neil.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.79,1:38:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对不起{\r}\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.87,1:38:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}尼尔 你有这个天才{\r}\NNeil. Neil. You have the gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.21,1:38:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}演得真好 我都看呆了{\r}\NWhat a performance. You left even me speechless.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.67,1:38:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你一定要坚持...  - 上车吧{\r}\N- You have to stay with...  - Get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.05,1:39:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}基丁 离我儿子远点儿{\r}\NKeating, you stay away from my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.76,1:39:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}尼尔 佩里先生 求你了{\r}\NNeil! Neil! Mr Perry, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.85,1:39:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别把事情越弄越糟{\r}\NDon't make it any worse than it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.69,1:39:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你想做另一辆车吗{\r}\NDo you want to take the other car?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.12,1:39:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们走回去行吗{\r}\NIs it okay if we walk back?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.53,1:39:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}船长{\r}\NCaptain?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.21,1:39:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 诺克斯  - 什么{\r}\N- Knox?  - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.71,1:39:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们11:30的时候就会到家{\r}\NWe'll be home about 11:30.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.00,1:40:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们一直在想你为什么{\r}\NWe're trying very hard...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.80,1:40:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}偏偏要违背我们的意思{\r}\Nto understand why it is that you insist on defying us.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.38,1:40:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但不管是什么原因 我们不会让你毁了自己一生{\r}\NBut whatever the reason, we're not gonna let you ruin your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.93,1:40:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}明天我就让你从这个学校退学 上布莱登军校{\r}\NI'm withdrawing you from Welton and enrolling you in Braden Military School.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.73,1:40:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你要上哈佛 你要成为一个医生{\r}\NYou're going to Harvard, and you're gonna be a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.94,1:40:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那还要十年{\r}\NBut that's ten more years.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.94,1:40:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 爸爸 那太漫长了  - 闭嘴{\r}\N- Father, that's a lifetime!  - Oh, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.07,1:40:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别夸张了 听上去像关你监狱似的{\r}\NDon't be so dramatic. You make it sound like a prison term.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.45,1:40:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你不明白 尼尔{\r}\NYou don't understand, Neil.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.45,1:40:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你有很好的机会 我做梦都没想过的好机会{\r}\NYou have opportunities that I never even dreamt of!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.46,1:40:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我不会让你错过  - 我要告诉你我是什么感觉{\r}\N- I am not going to let you waste them!  - I've got to tell you what I feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.54,1:40:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们很担心 要是...{\r}\NWe've been so worried about...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.14,1:40:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}什么 告诉我你的感觉{\r}\NWhat? What? Tell me what you feel!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.88,1:41:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}什么感觉{\r}\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.60,1:41:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是不是又是演戏这回事{\r}\NIs it more of this-this acting business?
