Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.08,1:55:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 梦想成为一个医生  - 不是这样的 卡梅伦{\r}\N- and dreaming of being called "Doctor"!  - That is not true, Cameron!
