Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.88,1:55:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 是尼尔自己喜欢演戏  - 你爱怎么想怎么想吧{\r}\N- Neil loved acting.  - Believe what you want,
