Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.22,1:55:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}干嘛毁了我们自己呢{\r}\NI mean, why ruin our lives?
