Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.20,1:55:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果你们其他人够聪明 就照我的做{\r}\NAnd if the rest of you are smart, you'll do exactly what I did!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.87,1:55:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}反正他们也全知道了{\r}\NThey know everything anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.95,1:55:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们救不了基丁{\r}\NYou can't save Keating,
