Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.50,1:56:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}诺克斯・奥弗斯特里特{\r}\NKnox Overstreet.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.53,1:56:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 米克斯  - 走开 我要学习{\r}\N- Meeks.  - Go away. I have to study.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.36,1:57:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}纽旺达怎么了{\r}\NWhat happened to Nuwanda?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.70,1:57:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}被开除了{\r}\NExpelled.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.37,1:57:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你跟他们说了什么{\r}\NWhat'd you tell 'em?
