Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.90,1:58:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我这儿有一份你们聚会的详细情况{\r}\NI have here a detailed description of what occurred at your meetings.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.58,1:58:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}里面谈到你们的老师 基丁{\r}\NIt describes how your teacher, Mr Keating,
