Dialogue: 0,1:58:28.58,1:58:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}并把它作为一个{\r}\Nand to use it as a source of inspiration
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.87,1:58:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}煽动鲁莽任性行为的中心{\r}\Nfor reckless and self-indulgent behaviour.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.59,1:58:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}还谈到基丁老师是如何在课内课外{\r}\NIt describes how Mr Keating, both in and out of the classroom,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:39.68,1:58:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}鼓动尼尔・佩里去演戏{\r}\Nencouraged Neil Perry to follow his obsession with acting...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.76,1:58:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}尽管他一直都知道这是违背他父母的明确规定的{\r}\Nwhen he knew all along it was against the explicit orders of Neil's parents.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.31,1:58:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}正是基丁老师滥用了他作为一个老师的影响力{\r}\NIt was Mr Keating's blatant abuse of his position as teacher...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.31,1:58:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}才导致了尼尔的死亡{\r}\Nthat led directly to Neil Perry's death.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.95,1:59:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}仔细看一下这份报告 托德{\r}\NRead that document carefully, Todd.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.13,1:59:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好好看看{\r}\NVery carefully.
