Dialogue: 0,1:59:40.70,1:59:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一幢楼叫埃迪菲西恩{\r}\NThe entire building is aedificium.
