Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.70,2:00:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这学期的英语课由我来上完{\r}\NI'll be teaching this class through exams.
