Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.89,2:00:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 呃 学到...  - 我听不清 安德森{\r}\N- Uh, in the, in the Prit...  - I can't hear you, Mr Anderson.
