Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.77,2:00:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你告诉我吧 卡梅伦{\r}\NKindly inform me, Mr Cameron.
