Dialogue: 0,2:02:54.15,2:02:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs22\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 走吧 基丁  - 这不是他的错{\r}\N- Leave, Mr Keating.  - But it wasn't his fault!
